data.description: Welcome to your forever vacation! A beautifully renovated 1 story home with a full finished basement. Enter and find yourself in an open concept main floor where you'll find a spacious living room with a fireplace, a newly renovated kitchen with quartz countertops, LED lighting, and plenty of storage. Continue into the large  dining room and enjoy your meal with the beautiful view overlooking the lake. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a finished basement you'll have enough space for all your loved ones. Step out onto the deck and enjoy the summer in the backyard with the hot tub, pool, pond, bonfire, and pier with direct access to the lake. Your 3 car garage can provide extra space for storage and warm cars in the winter. All furniture, appliances, and outdoor facilities to be included with the home!
